CONVENIENT ACCESS TO OUR GLOBAL PERSPECTIVE




















Many ways to invest



MUTUAL FUNDS
US-based investors can access our strategies through the Harding Loevner family of mutual funds, with share classes for institutions, advisers, and individual investors. 
UCITS FUNDS
European and other institutional investors based outside the US can invest in our strategies through Harding Loevner’s Irish-domiciled UCITS funds. 
AUSTRALIAN UNIT TRUSTS
Australian and New Zealand investors can invest in our strategies through Harding Loevner’s Unit Trusts.
 
 


SEPARATELY MANAGED ACCOUNTS
We offer each of our strategies to institutions worldwide through accounts managed separately to meet their unique needs. 
Collective Investment Trusts
US tax-qualified and governmental retirement plans can invest in our strategies efficiently under collective trust funds advised by Harding Loevner.


















  






